				<li><a href="../tag/t3a.html"><span class="tagM">T3A: Meta-languages</span></a> (<span class="info">5</span> times)</li>
				<li><a href="../tag/t4c.html"><span class="tagM">T4C: Vertical Transformation</span></a> (<span class="info">4</span> times)</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Top 3 coauthors:
			<ul>
				<li><a href="AdrianJohnstone.html"><span class="info">Adrian Johnstone</span></a> (<span class="info">8</span> times)</li>
